Package: randomizedexperiments
Type: Package
Title: Hierarchical Clustering Matching and Rerandomization for Causality
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Your Name
Maintainer: Your Name <your.email@example.com>
Description: Implementation of HCM (Hierarchical Clustering Matching), 
    HCM-ReR (Hierarchical Clustering Matching Re-Randomization), and 
    PWD-ReR (Principal component Weighted Distance Re-Randomization) methods for 
    generating balanced treatment allocations in randomized experiments. These methods 
    improve covariate balance while maintaining the randomization principle.
